message.content: cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SD, cs.CR, cs.SE because the paper discusses the impact of code cloning on software maintenance and correctness, which are topics related to software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper investigates the occurrence of faults induced by inconsistent changes to cloned code, which is relevant to computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper is based on a large-scale case study, which is a common approach in software engineering research (cs.SE).
